{"tid":810024,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"拿卡錫迪論FIFA值：我慢過Auba？","createTime":"2018-09-07T15:27:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-09T05:46:18.000Z","uid":147522,"like":38,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"d26c0a907a1bfaf5f210626e9987f6bf9e0fd38d","tid":810024,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T15:27:55.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=LACzl6Du%2FRWIbUjHR75B05ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=09ed6621\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】不管是真心嬲豬或是配合宣傳，球員不滿自己在《FIFA》電玩的數值已成指定動作，最新一人是阿仙奴的拿卡錫迪。<br />\n<br />\n《FIFA 19》將在9月28日推出，玩家自然磨拳擦掌等開波，但更緊張的似乎是球員本身，皆因遊戲給予自己的數值關乎面子，不平則鳴在所難免。 在生產商EA的最新宣傳片中，兵工廠的法國前鋒拿卡錫迪（Alexandre Lacazette）收到自己的《FIFA 19》數值卡，看到速度值時不禁驚訝：「唔係掛？我明明快過Auba好多喎。」只見他一臉怒容，把數值卡丢進廢紙箱，再丟下一句「話我唔夠快？我就快閃畀你睇」，然後一溜煙離開。 拿卡錫迪七情上面，令人忍俊不禁。他怒丟的數值卡顯示他平均值是85，但速度值不知是多少，又跟隊友奧巴美揚相差多少，需要如此動氣？"},{"pid":"2f988fb61686d95c596f449e0e3e24cd290863ff","tid":810024,"uid":68320,"like":1,"dislike":22,"score":-21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T15:29:09.000Z","msg":"好撚小氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8c180375de1d50e8be431194780b9e38eb53f97","tid":810024,"uid":27416,"like":58,"dislike":27,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T15:29:21.000Z","msg":"呢條廢西都85?"},{"pid":"9ea1dde72b42e14867d0a78085128043b4ba59f0","tid":810024,"uid":60695,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T17:33:32.000Z","msg":"有冇保特"},{"pid":"9841be2501ca21abc184fbb8354cdadab3f2ae48","tid":810024,"uid":165817,"like":49,"dislike":1,"score":48,"quote":{"pid":"2f988fb61686d95c596f449e0e3e24cd290863ff","tid":810024,"uid":68320,"like":1,"dislike":22,"score":-21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T15:29:09.000Z","msg":"好撚小氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src